\taxon{Definition}
\title{Structural sheaf on spectra}
\import{macro}

\p{
  For a distributive lattice #{D}, the structural sheaf #{\rg{D}} on #{\spec D} is given as follows: For each [basic open](idem-comm-CU42) #{O_p} of #{\spec D}, which we may simply write as #{p}, we define
  ##{ \rg{D}(p) := D/p. }
  For #{q \le p}, we put the restriction map to be
  ##{ q \wedge - : \rg{D}(p) \cong D/p \surj D/q \cong \rg{D}(q). }
}